No. 11-293. Jussi K. Kivisto, Petitioner v. Miller, Canfield, Paddock and Stone, PLC, et al. 565 U.S. 1045, 132 S. Ct. 577,

181 L. Ed. 2d 441,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8100. November 14, 2011.

Motion of petitioner to defer consideration of the petition for writ of certiorari denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied.

Same case below, 413 Fed. Appx. 136.
